           SHORT="Tool for terminal session {at,de}tach support"

cat << EOF
abduco provides session management i.e. it allows programs to be run
independently from their controlling terminal. That is programs can
be detached - run in the background - and then later reattached.
Together with dvtm it provides a simpler and cleaner alternative to
tmux or screen.
EOF
